source.name: Administrative Law Judge Opinions on Locomotive Engineers issued by the Federal Railroad Administration
source.description: These final opinions made in the adjudication of cases involve decisions by the Federal Railroad Administrator on appeals involving the agency's qualification and certification of locomotive engineers program pursuant to 49 C.F.R. ''§240.411.
